<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About GymGuru</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= asset_path 'application.css' %>">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f9;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 15px;
    }

    .header-section {
      background: url('your-about-hero-image.jpg') no-repeat center center;
      background-size: cover;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 80px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .header-section h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff7e5f, #feb47b, #ff7e5f);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      z-index: 2;
      position: relative;
      background-size: 200% 200%;
      animation: gradientShift 5s ease infinite, fadeInUp 1s ease-out;
    }

    @keyframes gradientShift {
      0% {
        background-position: 0% 50%;
      }
      50% {
        background-position: 100% 50%;
      }
      100% {
        background-position: 0% 50%;
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .header-section p {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-weight: 300;
      z-index: 2;
      position: relative;
      animation: fadeInUp 1.5s ease-out;
    }

    .content-section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .content-section .section-item {
      flex: 1 1 calc(50% - 20px); /* 50% width minus gap */
      box-sizing: border-box;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      text-align: center; /* Center text alignment */
    }

    .content-section .section-item:nth-of-type(1) {
      border: 2px solid #007bff; /* Blue border for the first item */
    }

    .content-section .section-item:nth-of-type(2) {
      border: 2px solid #ff7e5f; /* Orange border for the second item */
    }

    .content-section .section-item:nth-of-type(3) {
      border: 2px solid #28a745; /* Green border for the third item */
    }

    .content-section h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #333;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out, slideIn 1s ease-out;
      text-align: center; /* Center heading text */
    }

    .content-section p {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out;
      text-align: center; /* Center paragraph text */
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .content-section ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; /* Center list items */
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .content-section ul li {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-align: center; /* Center text in list items */
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @keyframes slideIn {
      from {
        transform: translateY(-20px);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      to {
        transform: translateY(0);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    .contact-section {
      background: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .contact-section h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
    }

    .contact-section p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out;
    }

    .contact-section a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      background: #fff;
      color: #007bff;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .contact-section a:hover {
      background: #0056b3;
      color: #fff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About GymGuru</h1>
      <p>Your ultimate destination for achieving fitness goals.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content-section">
    <div class="section-item">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>At GymGuru, our mission is to empower individuals to lead healthier lives through customized fitness solutions. We believe in the power of personalized plans that cater to your unique needs and preferences.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="section-item">
      <h2>What We Offer</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Personalized Workout Plans:</strong> Tailored routines designed to fit your goals, whether it's building muscle, losing weight, or enhancing endurance.</li>
        <li><strong>Diet Recommendations:</strong> Expert advice on nutrition and meal plans that complement your fitness regime.</li>
        <li><strong>Supplements:</strong> A curated selection of supplements to support your fitness journey.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section-item">
      <h2>Why Choose GymGuru?</h2>
      <p>Our team of fitness experts and nutritionists are dedicated to providing you with the best tools and resources to succeed. We use advanced algorithms and AI-driven insights to ensure that your plans are as effective and efficient as possible.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="contact-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>Have questions or need support? Reach out to our friendly customer service team at <%= mail_to 'support@gymguru.com' %>. Weâ€™re here to help you every step of the way.</p>
      <%= link_to 'Get Started Now', new_user_registration_path, class: 'cta-button' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
